---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="OpsHQ Digital privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="prose text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p>OpsHQ Digital ("we," "us," or "our") is operated by Nick Reef in Washington State. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit opshqdigital.com.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 mb-2">Contact Form Submissions</h3>
          <p>When you submit our contact form, we collect: name, email address, phone number (optional), company name (optional), service interest, project description, and UTM tracking parameters from the URL.</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 mt-4 mb-2">Analytics Data (With Your Consent)</h3>
          <p>If you accept analytics cookies, we collect page views, device information, and interaction data through Google Analytics 4 (GA4) and Microsoft Clarity. These tools are only loaded after you provide consent.</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 mt-4 mb-2">Cookies</h3>
          <p>We use only functional cookies by default. Analytics cookies from GA4 and Microsoft Clarity are loaded only after you provide explicit consent through our cookie banner.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to your inquiry</li>
            <li>Schedule and conduct discovery calls</li>
            <li>Send project proposals</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <p><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> Retained in Azure Table Storage for 90 days if unconverted (no project engagement). Manually reviewed and deleted on a 90-day cycle.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong>Active client data:</strong> Retained for duration of engagement plus 1 year.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Governed by Google and Microsoft retention policies (default 14 months for GA4).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — analytics, consent-gated</li>
            <li><strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong> — heatmaps and session recordings, consent-gated</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — DNS, CDN, and security</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> — spam prevention on contact form</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
          <p>Contact form submissions are stored in Azure Table Storage (Microsoft Azure, US data centers). No third-party form processors have access to your submission data. All data in transit is encrypted via TLS/HTTPS.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">If you are located outside the United States, your data may be transferred to and processed in the US.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data</li>
            <li>Withdraw analytics consent at any time via your browser settings or by clearing cookies</li>
            <li>Request information about data we hold about you</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:nick@opshqdigital.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600">nick@opshqdigital.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Material changes will be noted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related questions or data deletion requests:</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><a href="mailto:nick@opshqdigital.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600">nick@opshqdigital.com</a><br />Washington State, USA</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
